    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Insecurity and Welfare benefits"@nl, "Insecurity and Welfare benefits"@fr, "Insecurity and Welfare benefits"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "In Brussels as in the rest of Belgium, many people do not have sufficient means of subsistence. In some circumstances, these people may qualify for welfare benefits. These are aimed at ensuring that all the population has a minimum income."@nl, "In Brussels as in the rest of Belgium, many people do not have sufficient means of subsistence. In some circumstances, these people may qualify for welfare benefits. These are aimed at ensuring that all the population has a minimum income."@fr, "In Brussels as in the rest of Belgium, many people do not have sufficient means of subsistence. In some circumstances, these people may qualify for welfare benefits. These are aimed at ensuring that all the population has a minimum income."@en;
