<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0d3b150151222851b9cc9ab3327edb30>.
<#0d3b150151222851b9cc9ab3327edb30> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dist/brussels/38fdc66b98cda1a40e08edc7e5e7b019fdf10d73/5275de721813e271ae95098aaa789431cbaa1887>;
